    title: 'Topeng Panji',
    description:
      'Artefak budaya luhur Kerajaan Kediri yang mengangkat kisah cinta abadi Panji Asmarabangun & Galuh Candrakirana. Melambangkan karakter yang halus, bijaksana, penuh kasih, serta nilai kepahlawanan sejati.',
    imageUrl:
      'https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEglYegabv5cyoOM9OKM50IaCjxPEibHE5fHnfcsbf5uFilSCLz72Cn5oO70mLWEq8DFpmIkRybjVwpVsngF9B3ta6nAyJYujjBgt3PH1hBHKxBeN_U2WjhZAk-m5VAzxOrZDq2mbOP0cToDDsfIX_RIee8kQqIKyA19ZnM-XI_KgcABczufemK6k9CPOiav/s429-rw/ASSET%20MEDALI%20-%20TOPENG%20PANJI.png',
    tags: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'bendungan-waru-turi',
    title: 'Bendungan Waru Turi',
    description:
      'Bukan sekadar infrastruktur irigasi, Bendungan Gerak Waru Turi hadir sebagai simbol kemajuan, pusat edukasi masyarakat, dan kawasan wisata air yang menyatu dengan harmoni alam Kediri.',
    imageUrl:
      'https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZDEpPQwdtCmpxDn_zUHymIRvegAVpYQM9kMsnDNqMIPlacatdqpw2hKFdJFNFr-BjGCj5TlSg3zscx-bEtAx1zDmJEebeyW5V2Ja0-Zswwq8b78PRq0GAbFnAM7DJyK2LfkfGG_iOZ0_YSu4Rou35n0eLBpwHWpbFYbxyYrhAhLt-RO-WmhjKZQbzVsz1/s492-rw/ASSET%20MEDALI%20-%20ILUSTRASI%20BENDUNGAN%20GERAK%20WARU%20TURI.png',
    tags: [],
  },
  {
    id: 'batik-trinayana',
    title: 'Motif Batik Trinayana',
    description:
      'Perpaduan motif klasik dan modern yang memancarkan tiga masa: Mata Leluhur (Ingatan), Mata Diri (Keseimbangan Jiwa), dan Mata Masa Depan yang membara menembus batas cakrawala baru.',
    imageUrl:
      'https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhdDx0QmBmm8EoF2ZBpHqW46DyAj99CJRwiT9jdwG78-KYVpmTclLJs0pQZxMyqjJS_2hTwnZMQRy8xFYQHJrpHDT2Ux1L-2zyHQUBlQhFEXNmzzGZ4RIduVW68OF2LleQ8jFJ_SHLYXTk0fbjhCsfTjjyJkL3mwsdwq5yoIUwuIbmGq1Zxvl1ZIDenJFLU/s362-rw/ASSET%20MEDALI%20-%20KAIN%20BATIK%20TRINAYANA.png',
    tags: [],
  },
];

const conclusionText =
  '"Medali Waru Turi Fun Run 2026 adalah harmoni antara warisan budaya dan visi masa depan. Menggabungkan kemegahan Batik Trinayana, kearifan lokal Topeng Panji, dan vitalitas Bendungan Waru Turi sebagai simbol semangat perjuangan yang selaras dengan alam dan kemajuan zaman."';
---

<BaseLayout title="Medali Finisher Waru Turi Fun Run 2026" description="Medali Finisher Waru Turi Fun Run 2026 hadir dengan desain eksklusif sebagai simbol keberhasilan pelari yang menuntaskan kategori 5K dan 10K.">
  <Navbar />

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="race-hero">
    <div class="race-overlay"></div>
    <div class="race-hero-content">
      <h1 class="race-title">Medali Finisher Eksklusif</h1>
      <p class="race-subtitle">
        Dapatkan medali eksklusif bagi peserta yang menyelesaikan rute, dengan desain unik dan kualitas premium sebagai tanda prestasi.
      </p>
      <div class="race-breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span>›</span>
        <span>Medali</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== MEDAL SECTION ===== -->
  <section class="medal-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="medal-grid">
        {medalData.map((medal) => (
          <div key={medal.id} class="medal-card">
            <div class="medal-card-inner">
              <div class="medal-image-wrapper">
                <img
                  src={medal.imageUrl}
                  alt={medal.title}
                  class="medal-image"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <span class="medal-badge">
                  <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i> Exclusive
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="medal-content">
                <h3 class="medal-title">{medal.title}</h3>
                <div class="medal-description" set:html={medal.description}></div>
                <div class="medal-tags">
                  <span class="medal-tag">
                    <i class="bi bi-trophy"></i> Finisher
                  </span>
                  <span class="medal-tag gold-tag">
                    <i class="bi bi-award"></i> Edisi Terbatas
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== FILOSOFI ===== -->
  <section class="filosofi-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Filosofi Medali 2026</h2>
        <div class="section-line"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="filosofi-grid">
        {philosophyItems.map((item, index) => (
          <div key={item.id} class={`filosofi-item ${index % 2 === 0 ? '' : 'reverse'}`}>
            <div class="filosofi-image">
              <img src={item.imageUrl} alt={item.title} loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="filosofi-content">
              <h3>{item.title}</h3>
              <p>{item.description}</p>
              {item.tags && item.tags.length > 0 && (
                <div class="filosofi-tags">
                  {item.tags.map((tag) => (
                    <span key={tag} class="filosofi-tag">{tag}</span>
                  ))}
                </div>
              )}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="filosofi-conclusion">
        <h3>Makna Filosofis Medali</h3>
        <p>{conclusionText}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Raih Medali <span>Eksklusif</span> Anda!</h2>
        <p>Daftar sekarang dan jadilah bagian dari sejarah Waru Turi Fun Run 2026. Medali terbatas hanya untuk peserta tercepat!</p>
        <a href="/p/ticket-sold.html" class="cta-button">
          <i class="bi bi-trophy"></i> Daftar Sekarang
        </a>
        <p class="cta-note">
          <i class="bi bi-clock-history"></i> Kuota terbatas, segera daftar!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== CONTAINER ===== */
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .race-hero {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 320px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11, 124, 255, 0.85), rgba(0, 182, 219, 0.85)),
      url('https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhLgtAHbzolMJkhEg_42wG0oVMGz24ls7ax9m3XUknvO8pkQA6NK93M3Opv9zTOczYPgXH1f92LEGnrmKRFA5JoG9W7Yj8MwGXouQ64OBF6A4IrjBcO_g_0576t4CPIlxVYzu3kLEvdI6tyP8D44Je7U7sRmo_aYGXc_Pgq5R0y9oJoRXtA2GjOrW-xXTiJ/s1280/header.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }
  
  .race-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .race-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 700px;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  
  .race-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  
  .race-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #e0f7fa;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 550px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  .race-breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #e0f7fa;
  }
  
  .race-breadcrumb a {
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .race-breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #FFD700;
  }
  
  .race-breadcrumb span {
    margin: 0 6px;
  }

  /* ===== MEDAL SECTION ===== */
  .medal-section {
    padding: 60px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  
  .medal-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 30px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .medal-card {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }
  
  .medal-card:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.15s;
  }
  
  .medal-card-inner {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    padding: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 30px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .medal-card-inner:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(38, 121, 236, 0.12);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: rgba(38, 121, 236, 0.15);
  }
  
  .medal-image-wrapper {
    flex: 0 0 200px;
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4ff, #e8edf5);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .medal-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 180px;
    object-fit: contain;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  
  .medal-card-inner:hover .medal-image {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  
  .medal-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -6px;
    right: -6px;
    background: #FFD700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  
  .medal-badge i {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
  }
  
  .medal-content {
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  .medal-title {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #2679ec;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  
  .medal-description {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #4a4a4a;
  }
  
  .medal-description b {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }
  
  .medal-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  
  .medal-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    background: rgba(38, 121, 236, 0.08);
    color: #2679ec;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .medal-tag i {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  .gold-tag {
    background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.12);
    color: #996600;
  }

  /* ===== FILOSOFI SECTION ===== */
  .filosofi-section {
    padding: 60px 0;
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }
  
  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #2679ec;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  
  .section-line {
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: #d4af37;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  
  .filosofi-grid {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  
  .filosofi-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .filosofi-item:hover {
    background: #f0f4ff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }
  
  .filosofi-item.reverse {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }
  
  .filosofi-image {
    flex: 0 0 160px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .filosofi-image img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 160px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .filosofi-item:hover .filosofi-image img {
    transform: scale(1.04);
  }
  
  .filosofi-content {
    flex: 1;
  }
  
  .filosofi-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #2679ec;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  
  .filosofi-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  
  .filosofi-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  
  .filosofi-tag {
    padding: 4px 14px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 2px solid #e8edf5;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }
  
  .filosofi-conclusion {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 50px auto 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2679ec, #1a5bb5);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 40px 48px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(38, 121, 236, 0.25);
  }
  
  .filosofi-conclusion h3 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #FFD700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  
  .filosofi-conclusion p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ===== CTA SECTION ===== */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 50px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #001a4d, #0033A0);
  }
  
  .cta-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  
  .cta-content h2 span {
    color: #FFD700;
  }
  
  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: #FFD700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #FFC107;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4);
  }
  
  .cta-button i {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .cta-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) !important;
    margin-top: 12px !important;
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }
  
  .cta-note i {
    margin-right: 4px;
  }

  /* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  
  .filosofi-item {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }
  
  .filosofi-item:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
  }
  
  .filosofi-item:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }
  
  .filosofi-item:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }
  
  .filosofi-conclusion {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.4s;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .medal-card-inner {
      padding: 20px;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    
    .medal-image-wrapper {
      flex: 0 0 160px;
    }
    
    .filosofi-item {
      padding: 20px;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    
    .filosofi-image {
      flex: 0 0 130px;
    }
    
    .filosofi-image img {
      max-width: 130px;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .race-hero {
      min-height: 260px;
    }
    
    .race-title {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    
    .race-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .medal-section {
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    
    .medal-grid {
      gap: 20px;
    }
    
    .medal-card-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 20px;
      gap: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .medal-image-wrapper {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 200px;
      padding: 12px;
    }
    
    .medal-image {
      max-height: 140px;
    }
    
    .medal-title {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
    
    .medal-description {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .medal-tags {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .filosofi-section {
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    
    .filosofi-grid {
      gap: 24px;
    }
    
    .filosofi-item {
      flex-direction: column !important;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    
    .filosofi-item.reverse {
      flex-direction: column !important;
    }
    
    .filosofi-image {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 140px;
